{"tid":1981832,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【疫市開舖】日本Sukiya油麻地譽發廣場開分店 月租25萬","createTime":"2020-04-21T01:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T04:52:12.000Z","uid":1121,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e684bd5bdf34c77f1cc45bfb950c63b96c508e39","tid":1981832,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2620000/2622535/sukiya_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2620000%2F2622535%2Fsukiya_1024.jpg&h=12a27d71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本食店日本牛肉飯連鎖店Sukiya（すき家/食其家）疫市擴充，將於油麻地譽發廣場地下開設香港第2家分店。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士透露，Sukiya以承租油麻地譽發廣場地下舖位，面積約2,650平方呎，月租約25萬元。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，Sukiya去年以約22萬元月租承租旺角亞皆老街31號地舖，由日本公司營運，並於去年底開業，大排長龍，當時更以24小時營運，惟今年1月初宣布改為早時6時至凌晨12時30分。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意，競爭對手之一的吉野家，位於油麻地的分店日前結業，業主在店外所貼告示指，吉野家在去年12月起一直欠租已四個月。"},{"pid":"4a1069ebe2c7f8f12e00ee98282bf0b481393649","tid":1981832,"uid":1121,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2620000/2622535/dcmn20170611600_2500x2500_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2620000%2F2622535%2Fdcmn20170611600_2500x2500_1024.jpg&h=c5641353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 油麻地譽發廣場地下租戶曾多次轉人，包括內衣店、日用品店。"},{"pid":"e85aac4abdbb6fbf51615e92184f42bc67f7687f","tid":1981832,"uid":65747,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:45:26.000Z","msg":"lam埋吉野家個位喇屌你"},{"pid":"0d832ae601a2d07f998cd964337c6d95c2403d9d","tid":1981832,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e85aac4abdbb6fbf51615e92184f42bc67f7687f","tid":1981832,"uid":65747,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:45:26.000Z","msg":"lam埋吉野家個位喇屌你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2